<main class="ui two column stackable page grid">
<div class="column">
<div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">What is this?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">A website where you can ask questions to other users and answer their answers. You can control who can ask questions to you and who can see your answers.</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">How can I search for questions or users?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">Go to the <a href="search">Search</a> page</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">Do I need to create an account to ask questions?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">It depends on who you want to ask. Some users let everyone ask them, whereas some require an account.</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">Do I need an account to answer?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">Yes. How would others be able to ask you if you didn't have one?</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">Who can view questions I have answered?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">You can manage this in your <a href="settings">settings</a>. By default only your friends can.</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">Who can ask me a question?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">You can manage this in your <a href="settings">settings</a>. By default only your friends can.</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">What should I do if a question or answer is annoying me?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">If a question asked to you is annoying you, delete it. Otherwise, report it to us by clicking the 'Report' link.</p></div>
</div><div class="column">
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">What about copyright?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">All rights are reserved by each question/answer's author. When asking or answering make sure that you are the owner of what you upload. See the <a href="terms">Terms</a> for more.</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">How can I change my account info, friends and password?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">Go to <a href="settings">Settings</a>.</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">Who made this website?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">As of now, Anestis Varsamidis. His sister and father also helped him with some issues.</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">How can I delete my account?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">Go to <a href="settings">Settings</a> and click 'Delete my account'.</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">Can I see the source code? Can I help you on an issue?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">Sure! Just go to our <a href="https://github.com/anestv/pa/">GitHub page</a>!</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">Where can I report a bug or suggest a new feature?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">At our <a href="https://github.com/anestv/pa/issues">issues</a> page on GitHub.</p></div>
  <div class="faq"><h3 class="ui top attached purple header">What if I have a question that's not in this list?</h3>
  <p class="ui bottom attached stacked segment">Ask it at the <a href="user/privateask">PrivateAsk profile</a> or <a href="<?=CONTACT_URL?>">contact us</a>!</p></div>
</div></main>

